{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_14_02",
  "title": "早坂芽衣",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "なんてことだ……いくらアンダーグラウンドなエンタメ\nとはいえ、人に電流を流した挙句、爆破するなんて……",
      "startTime": 4.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon",
      "startTime": 8.966666317
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "見た目は派手だけど、安全には配慮してるみたいだから\n大丈夫だよ～！　本当はあの人達も無傷だよ！",
      "startTime": 12.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あんなに凄い爆発で、無傷なんてことあるのか！？\nもしや、ここの試合は全部あんな感じ……だったり？",
      "startTime": 20.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon",
      "startTime": 25.2333339692
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "『鎖鎌』って言うグループが始めたんだって。負けた\nアイドルを電流爆破したら盛り上がるんじゃないかって",
      "startTime": 29.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon",
      "startTime": 33.4333336195
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なぜだ……というか『鎖鎌』って気のせいじゃなければ\nVENUSプログラムの元上位ランカーだよな",
      "startTime": 37.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう！　その時からステージを爆破し続けて\n除名されちゃった伝説のアイドルだよー！",
      "startTime": 44.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon",
      "startTime": 47.6666694641
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣の最近の推しでもあるんだよ！　野良アイドルに\nなっても信念を貫き通して、カッコいいよね！",
      "startTime": 51.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon",
      "startTime": 55.8666710219
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、雫も前に話していた気がするな……\n『鎖鎌』にとって電流爆破は譲れない矜持なんだろうな",
      "startTime": 60.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "しかし、そうか、あの『鎖鎌』がいるなら非公式なのに\nここまで人が集まっている理由も頷けるよ",
      "startTime": 69.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon",
      "startTime": 72.9666656494
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "昔は『鎖鎌』だけじゃなくって、雫ちゃんが大好きな\nラッパー系アイドルの『リリック喫茶』もいたんだって",
      "startTime": 77.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon",
      "startTime": 80.8666702271
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふっふ、それに芽衣の調査によると\n『どりきゅん』も参加していた可能性があってねー",
      "startTime": 84.9000035604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon",
      "startTime": 87.9333458266
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "『どりきゅん』も！？　いや、だとしても……\n芽衣達をこんな過激な場所には出せないぞ",
      "startTime": 91,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "『鎖鎌』にばりばりどっかーんされる芽衣達なんて\n俺は見たくない",
      "startTime": 97,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon",
      "startTime": 98.6333384196
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "むう、{user}さんは\n芽衣達が負けるって思ってるの？",
      "startTime": 100.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon",
      "startTime": 103.3333463353
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "万が一の話をしただけだ\nとにかく、俺は参加してほしくないな",
      "startTime": 105.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "そんなぁ……もう千紗ちゃんには衣装作りを\nお願いしちゃってるし、曲の方も順調なのに……",
      "startTime": 112.8252198493,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon",
      "startTime": 117.7999979655
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "そうだっ！　じゃあ{user}さんも\nみんなに内緒で出演してみればいいんじゃないかな！",
      "startTime": 120.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてそうなった！？\n全然流れが分からないぞ！？",
      "startTime": 125.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon",
      "startTime": 127.3666641235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "だって直接見てもこの魅力が伝わらないなら\n一緒に参加してドキドキを体験するしかないよー！",
      "startTime": 131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫、{user}さんも楽しめるから！\nアイドルへの愛があれば参加出来るよ～！",
      "startTime": 138.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon",
      "startTime": 142.5000257175
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……まぁ、確かに参加者なら\n傍にいられるし、何かあった時に融通が利く……か？",
      "startTime": 145.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon",
      "startTime": 150.9666737874
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "わーい！　じゃあ決まりだね！　あははっ！\n{user}さんとバトル出来るかもだー！",
      "startTime": 155.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5866.6665792,
          "startTime": 161.5666665792
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7000.000087500012,
          "startTime": 162.7000000875
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8200.0000875,
          "startTime": 163.9000000875
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ま、待て、芽衣！　俺はまだ参加するとは一言も……\nひ、引っ張るな～～～～！",
      "startTime": 162.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 166.2666768392,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 167.3000183106
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "あの時は、なんとか芽衣を振り切って逃げられたが\n結局、出場するハメになるとは……",
      "startTime": 171.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "ソロでの出場が認められていないと知った時は\n参加しないで済むかとも思ったんだがな……",
      "startTime": 177.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "受付にいたMCの鈴木さんがノリノリで良かったよー！\nまさかその場でユニットを組んでくれるなんてね！",
      "startTime": 185.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、こうなったらもう後には引けないよ\n作詞や作曲、振り付けと、やることは山積みだけどな",
      "startTime": 192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣も出場するし、あんまり手伝えないけど\n出来る限り、サポートしてあげるよ！",
      "startTime": 200.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "助かるよ。よし、腹をくくって、やるからには本気だ\n胸を貸してくれ、芽衣！",
      "startTime": 207.8,
